subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: Tamika Catchings scored 8 of her 30 points in overtime, including the tying free throw with 14 seconds left and the winning jumper with a tenth of a second to go in the Indiana Fever's 80-78 victory over the Liberty at Madison Square Garden last night.
